<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق وض:</span> <span class="c2">(قَوَّضَ)</span> الْبِنَاءَ تَقْوِيضًا نَقَضَهُ مِنْ غَيْرِ هَدْمٍ. وَ <span class="c2">(تَقَوَّضَتِ)</span> الْحَلِقُ وَالصُّفُوفُ انْتَقَضَتْ وَتَفَرَّقَتْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>